From dc93bb3e56821098ec002a990ed58fe6c45a7641 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Apr 2026 20:02:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Fix Python 3.12 / modern scipy/numpy compatibility (based
 on dev branch)

- Remove 'import scipy.misc' from core.py (module removed in modern scipy)
- Replace np.bool with np.bool_ (removed in NumPy 2.x)
- Replace np.int with np.int_ (removed in NumPy 2.x)
- Replace np.alltrue with np.all (removed in NumPy 2.x)
- Replace np.random.random_integers with np.random.randint (removed in NumPy 2.x)
- Replace Delaunay.vertices with Delaunay.simplices (scipy rename)
- Fix invalid escape sequence in stos_brute.py
- Fix bare module imports in test files (setup_imagetest, test_assemble_tiles, volume)
- Add NORNIR_TEST_AUTOPASS support to ShowGrayscale and ShowWithPassFail for headless CI
